{"tid":1938572,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"周子瑜專屬影片深夜曝光！躺床上「女友視角」特寫鏡頭超撩人","createTime":"2020-03-22T15:35:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T00:21:35.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d630ae5c889d1af1649d9f67af96ddd7dd789fd4","tid":1938572,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:35:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vb18rzA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVb18rzA.jpg&h=8bfb5549&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昨天晚間周子瑜母校發表一段貼文，內容大大感謝周子瑜低調行善，捐款給清寒家庭的學弟妹，同一時間，周子瑜所經紀公司推特發表一段周子瑜專屬影片，36 秒的特寫鏡頭美到逆天，讓許多網友大讚人美心善。<br />\n<br />\n日前周子瑜各捐款給韓國、中國的武漢肺炎相關單位的善行引起好評，事隔幾週，周子瑜的母校，台南市立復興國中臉書粉專於昨天晚間發表一段貼文，內容指出，周子瑜於今年初低調行善，默默捐款給復興國中家境清寒的學弟妹，讓他們可以安心就學，讓人再次見識到周子瑜的為善不欲人知的美意。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/03/22/200322-13078-2-YsG6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F03%2F22%2F200322-13078-2-YsG6h.jpg&h=b3bf2a73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而就在昨晚母校發文的幾乎同一時間，周子瑜所屬經紀公司 JYP 娛樂也在專屬推特上，發表一段子瑜專屬影片，36 秒的特寫鏡頭，讓粉絲看得如癡如醉，尤其是當中周子瑜在床上、掀開被子的橋段，被網友讚為「超甜女友視角」，紛紛留言表示「這女友視角太撩了」、「誰拍的？犯規啦」、「哪裡找這種人美心善的小可愛」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/03/22/200322-13078-3-o6d8h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F03%2F22%2F200322-13078-3-o6d8h.jpg&h=1e138e0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/03/22/200322-13078-4-IwZRJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F03%2F22%2F200322-13078-4-IwZRJ.jpg&h=9f304060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周子瑜經紀公司發布最新個人專屬影片，其中躺在床上的「女友視角」被粉絲大讚超甜。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/03/22/200322-13078-5-TT9PN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F03%2F22%2F200322-13078-5-TT9PN.jpg&h=1f9a3ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周子瑜簡約的服裝及妝髮，都讓這支影片大大加分。<br />\n<br />\n影片中可見周子瑜身穿柔和的白色系服裝，搭配亞麻色的長鬈髮造型，搽上蜜桃色紅唇，多次對著鏡頭微笑、放電，成為昨天深夜網友討論的話題，更有粉絲直呼「大半夜的看這影片是要怎麼睡」。<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: blue;\"><br />\n【點影片】</span></ins></strong>"},{"pid":"62f61f08a9f22b0530fbf14c1e52c93e92998ee3","tid":1938572,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:40:10.000Z","msg":"睇返佢最近啲相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c458bfbe859b70cf6a3118c68d7f1c36fd7c1671","tid":1938572,"uid":217211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:42:55.000Z","msg":"片呢屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7928540721fcb51d09d3fcd1422a2f9cd6b478","tid":1938572,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:43:42.000Z","msg":"戀愛了"},{"pid":"b9bb381d869e27b885e7e37a9d0bd36eb0f84740","tid":1938572,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:44:37.000Z","msg":"不了<br />\n定延已係床到等我"},{"pid":"9f032cdc29866eb374fafa6b8312e6d56797e80e","tid":1938572,"uid":57035,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:45:11.000Z","msg":"修羅象腿"},{"pid":"35e560c4888fcdce10de3daf2a606843b58e1d2b","tid":1938572,"uid":137569,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:46:14.000Z","msg":"點解明明T寶後生咁多<br />\n偍好似快殘過rv咁多"},{"pid":"a3c47ad9b8d5201484d964fc535209db968683f9","tid":1938572,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:47:11.000Z","msg":"勁令==<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2EyZyiq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2EyZyiq.jpg&h=0630201f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2e07dff0c5e6355dd7669c0b27e5a2eca93c577","tid":1938572,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":1,